ActPooled Registered Pension Plans Act
SubjectOrder Approving that the Minister of Finance enter into the Multilateral Agreement Respecting Pooled Registered Pension Plans and Voluntary Retirement Savings Plans
PrecisOrder approving that the Minister of Finance to into an AGREEMENT with QUEBEC, NOVA SCOTIA, BRITISH COLUMBIA and SASKATCHEWAN, entitled the MULTILATERAL AGREEMENT RESPECTING POOLED REGISTERED PENSION PLANS AND VOLUNTARY RETIREMENT SAVINGS PLANS, effective June 7, 2016.
